name: hasExpirationDate
label: has expiration date
definition: links something, typically an agreement, contract, document, or perishable item, with an expiration date

name: hasReportingPeriod
label: has reporting period
definition: specifies the reporting period for which a report or something else, such as a market rate or economic indicator, applies

name: hasTerminationDate
label: has termination date
definition: links something, typically an agreement, contract, document, or process, with a date on which it was terminated

name: hasRecord
label: has record
definition: links something to a record that pertains to it
